<br />

<br />
Do you want to be self-reliant?
<br />

<br />
Do you want to be high on the list of classes groups pick up?
<br />

<br />
Do you want to be able to chat while playing?
<br />

<br />
Do you like playing a support role?
<br />

<br />
Do you like being a jack of all trades or a god in one type of skill?
<br />

<br />
