				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: highly indecisive- i need opinions.<a name="55416"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 9:34 AM</span></td>
